OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776395018
OL,3,CMurderer Iain Packer likely committed
OL,4,Cfurther sex crimes abroad, says
OL,5,Csurvivor
OL,7,FThe man convicted of killing Emma
OL,8,FCaldwell as well as a string of sexual
OL,9,Foffences against other women likely
OL,10,Fcommitted further crimes abroad,
OL,11,Faccording to one of his victims and a
OL,12,Fformer detective.
OL,14,FMagdalene Robertson said that she
OL,15,Fbelieved Iain Packer would have
OL,16,Fcommitted crimes against women while
OL,17,Fon holiday in Florida.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
