PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776395018
OL,3,CMurderer Iain Packer likely committed
OL,4,Cfurther sex crimes abroad, says
OL,5,Csurvivor
OL,7,FShe was indecently assaulted by Packer
OL,8,Fwhen she was 14 and raped by him when
OL,9,Fshe was 15. She told police about him
OL,10,Fin 2006.
OL,12,FMs Caldwell, 27, was killed in 2005
OL,13,Fbut it was not until 2024 that Packer
OL,14,Fwas convicted of her murder, along
OL,15,Fwith a string of sexual offences
OL,16,Fagainst other women.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
