PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776395018
OL,3,CMurderer Iain Packer likely committed
OL,4,Cfurther sex crimes abroad, says
OL,5,Csurvivor
OL,7,FMs Robertson spoke to Clyde 1's Beware
OL,8,FBook podcast series, which is
OL,9,Fexamining the death of Ms Caldwell and
OL,10,Fthose of other women involved in
OL,11,Fprostitution around Glasgow during the
OL,12,F1990s and 2000s.
OL,14,FThe podcast takes its name from a
OL,15,Fjournal which was used by women
OL,16,Finvolved in prostitution to warn each
OL,17,Fother about potentially dangerous or
OL,18,Fsuspicious clients.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
