PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776395018
OL,3,CMurderer Iain Packer likely committed
OL,4,Cfurther sex crimes abroad, says
OL,5,Csurvivor
OL,7,FMs Robertson, who has waived her right
OL,8,Fto anonymity, described Packer as an
OL,9,F"incubus" ` saying he was "somebody
OL,10,Fthat sucks the absolute life and the
OL,11,Fjoy out of any circumstance
OL,12,Fwhatsoever".
OL,14,FShe said she was sure Packer had
OL,15,Fcommitted previous offences against
OL,16,Fwomen and girls before he attacked her.
OL,18,FShe told the podcast: "They've always
OL,19,Fwent to Florida, Boxing Day, they went
OL,20,Fthere every year for two years.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@IO]qD@[OUtD@KO]zD@WOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
