PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776395018
OL,3,CMurderer Iain Packer likely committed
OL,4,Cfurther sex crimes abroad, says
OL,5,Csurvivor
OL,7,F"So, he's been attacking people
OL,8,Fbecause you don't be a serial rapist
OL,9,Fand sexual offender and say, 'I'm on
OL,10,Fholiday from that'.
OL,12,F"Your habits go with you."
OL,14,FShe added: "He would have been
OL,15,Fdefinitely within the sex clubs or the
OL,16,Fstrip clubs or what have you there as
OL,17,Fwell. And he's probably abused people
OL,18,Fin the hotel.
OL,20,F"I make that assumption. I would bet
OL,21,Fmoney on it."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUtD@ZO]vD@LOU|D@AOU}D@MO]
