OL,3,CMurderer Iain Packer likely committed
OL,4,Cfurther sex crimes abroad, says
OL,5,Csurvivor
OL,7,FMs Robertson said she had passed on
OL,8,Fher concerns to the FBI and was
OL,9,Fconsidering hiring a private
OL,10,Finvestigator to find out more about
OL,11,FPacker's time in the US.
OL,13,FShe also said she believed that the
OL,14,Fpolice investigation into Packer had
OL,15,Fdiscussed going to Spain at one point.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
