PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776395018
OL,3,CMurderer Iain Packer likely committed
OL,4,Cfurther sex crimes abroad, says
OL,5,Csurvivor
OL,7,FMeanwhile, retired detective constable
OL,8,FStuart Hall, who was involved in the
OL,9,Finitial investigation into Ms
OL,10,FCaldwell's murder, also said he
OL,11,Fbelieved that Packer had committed
OL,12,Foffences abroad.
OL,14,FHe had earlier told the podcast series
OL,15,Fthat the murder of Ms Caldwell was
OL,16,Flikely not the first killing carried
OL,17,Fout by Packer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
