OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776395018
OL,3,CMurderer Iain Packer likely committed
OL,4,Cfurther sex crimes abroad, says
OL,5,Csurvivor
OL,7,FMr Hall said: "When people go on
OL,8,Fholiday, they go on holiday to relax,
OL,9,Fto let their hair down, to, you know.
OL,10,FSo I don't see him going to stop any
OL,11,Fpattern of behaviour. That's who he
OL,12,Fis...
OL,14,F"So, absolutely. There'll be more in
OL,15,Fthis country and I think wherever he's
OL,16,Fholidayed."
OL,18,FPacker was jailed for life with a
OL,19,Fminimum term of 36 years after he was
OL,20,Ffound guilty of Ms Caldwell's murder.
OL,26,@oD@OOUvD@AOUxD@KO]
