OL,5,Csurvivor
OL,7,FHer body was found at a remote
OL,8,Flocation in Limefield Woods in South
OL,9,FLanarkshire.
OL,11,FA public inquiry, chaired by Lord
OL,12,FScott KC, is due to examine the police
OL,13,Finvestigation into the murder.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
