OL,3,CMurderer Iain Packer likely committed
OL,4,Cfurther sex crimes abroad, says
OL,5,Csurvivor
OL,7,FPolice Scotland Deputy Chief Constable
OL,8,FAlan Speirs said earlier: "Emma
OL,9,FCaldwell's family have shown
OL,10,Fincredible courage and determination
OL,11,Ffollowing her murder in 2005 and we
OL,12,Fare absolutely committed to supporting
OL,13,Fthe inquiry and getting her loved ones
OL,14,Fthe answers they deserve."
